                                    "insc_pntr": ">>",
                                    "insc_cntn": "If God became incarnate in His Son, Jesus Christ,\n\tand if we also are God's children,\n\t\tand if He is our Brother (as Jesus so often said),\n\n\t\t\t<b><i>then what does that say about us?</b></i>"
